Class Partition

  • java.lang.Object
    • sailpoint.tools.xml.AbstractXmlObject
      • sailpoint.object.Partition
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, org.json.JSONString, sailpoint.tools.xml.PersistentXmlObject

    public class Partition
extends AbstractXmlObject
implements org.json.JSONString
    A Partition is an XML/JSON object that is used by the connector interface to describe slices of data that can be split up.
    See Also:
    Connector.getIteratorPartitions(String, int, sailpoint.object.Filter, java.util.Map), Serialized Form
